snippet.title: S.T.A.L.K.E.R. 2: Heart of Chornobyl — Bolts & Bullets Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look around! Looks like the same old Zone, at a first glance… Freezed at the time and always transforming, primed to struck at the unforeseeable moment. But don’t let her trick you: She has changed from the last time you were here. And to let the stalker survive, she’ll demand the same! 

New S.T.A.L.K.E.R. 2: Heart of Chornobyl — Bolts & Bullets Trailer for your preparations to the upcoming adventure. 

Pre-order on PC: https://bit.ly/3Wg6AGC
Pre-order on Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-ultimate-edition-pre-order/9NJ1V5MDNWP2/0017
